{"tid":858101,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【含淚賣樓】盈翠半島勁劈21%易手 代理:股災打擊業主","createTime":"2018-10-11T14:19:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-13T15:17:53.000Z","uid":174649,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"5798f608cb399af85550ed36843e2aeacfae8212","tid":858101,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T14:19:41.000Z","msg":"美聯物業梁文楓表示，青衣樓王盈翠半島錄得本月首宗成交，屬大劈價，為12座低層E室，實用面積761方呎，三房間隔，業主最初放盤1,650萬元，最終堅持不了股票市場動盪，面對現實，施政報告後大幅減價21%最後成交價1,320萬元，呎價17,346元，較市價1,488萬元低11%或168萬元。他又指，近期樓價急挫，加息並非最主要因素，「其實最重要係個股市令到業主減價」。<br />\n中原地產梁岳宏亦指，上述放盤座向東南，享有維港海景，業主最終含淚大幅減價才能沽貨。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181011/large/1539266753_985d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181011%2Flarge%2F1539266753_985d.jpg&h=b1d5f04c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"689a3a8a8e479781a93c9b8f2f5381e48cbb62f7","tid":858101,"uid":40478,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T14:21:57.000Z","msg":"業主炒窿股票唔計"},{"pid":"112eff5776dedeb9f826e0f198bb5bbb84105ad5","tid":858101,"uid":122377,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T14:21:58.000Z","msg":"呢排個個業主都喊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be771ac7171c0cc39659ba4ae419bb3e48a36567","tid":858101,"uid":17765,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T14:25:34.000Z","msg":"劈價唔計"},{"pid":"b56639723e3f32f79c9a55c6e9fd49e17c2f52b3","tid":858101,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T14:27:34.000Z","msg":"又劈到喊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f77889437bd52c629183d74dfa592d8fa23f9f93","tid":858101,"uid":137725,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T14:27:45.000Z","msg":"業主喊, 成個小朋友咁, 唔計"},{"pid":"4809a01a54bd7894cbed2eda088b